One of the company's internal regulations says that they will not announce any new service in advance, but only when it is ready to work, which if it is certain that the foreseeable problems of the coming months and years will be able to stir the world: while some believe that Google's book and magazine scanning and archiving project will acquire such dimensions that the company will soon be cited by the U.S. Supreme Court, others fear its Health system, because in it we can create our own complete health profile, with previous analyses, with our doctors and our problems.
